pr_body:
Ref #24200 
Changes made -
1. Optimized MySQL grammar file for Collate expression
2. Created a Converter file for collate expression
3. Since Calcite only support of ISO type as Collate naming format, The approach for this PR is avoiding the use of Calcite's SqlCollation class & Using an alternative way of calling SqlBasicCall class to perform the task.
